title: Bp069_Active UC W0_IFX_43
source_name_ch1: Colonic mucosal biopsy from active UC patient 43 before infliximab (IFX) therapy
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted using the RNeasy Mini Kit (Qiagen, Benelux B.V.), according to the manufacturer’s instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotin-labeled single-stranded DNA was synthesized using the Affymetrix GeneChip WT terminal Labeling kit (Affymetrix), according to manufacturer's instructions.
hyb_protocol: After fragmentation of DNA, labeled DNA was hybridized for 16h at 45°C on Affymetrix Human Gene 1.0 ST arrays.
scan_protocol: The arrays were washed and stained in a fluidics station using the GeneChip hybridization, Wash end Stain kit (Affymetrix) and scanned using the Affymetrix 3000 GeneScanner.
description: Colonic mucosal biopsy from active UC patient 43 before infliximab (IFX) therapy
data_processing: Probe level analysis was performed on the Affymetrix raw data (.cel files) with the robust multichip average (RMA) method implemented in the Bioconductor package 'aroma.affymetrix' to obtain a log2 expression value for each gene probe set
